#: ../../N/netburp.rst:5
msgid "netburp"
msgstr "netburp"

#: ../../N/netburp.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../N/netburp.rst:9
msgid ""
"[IRC] When :ref:`netlag` gets really bad, and delays between servers exceed "
"a certain threshold, the :ref:`IRC` network effectively becomes partitioned "
"for a period of time, and large numbers of people seem to be signing off at "
"the same time and then signing back on again when things get better. An "
"instance of this is called a netburp (or, sometimes, :ref:`netsplit`\\)."
msgstr ""
"[IRC] \\ :ref:`netlag`\\ が本当にひどくなり、サーバー間の遅延がある閾値を超えると、\\ :ref:`IRC`\\ "
"ネットワークが一定期間事実上分断され、多数の人々が同時にサインオフし、状況が改善するとまた一斉にサインオンし直すように見える。この一例をnetburp(あるいは時に\\"
" :ref:`netsplit`\\ )と呼ぶ。"
